OL,3,CFarmers' protest: 'I've never seen
OL,4,Cfarmers come together with such
OL,5,Cemotion'
OL,7,FOver the last three generations,
OL,8,FMontague Farm in East Sussex has been
OL,9,Ftransformed from a derelict, unviable
OL,10,Fbusiness into an organic beef and lamb
OL,11,Ffarm which has nature recovery at its
OL,12,Fheart.
OL,14,FMartin Hole took over the running of
OL,15,Fthe business from his father-in-law
OL,16,Fwhen he retired at 90 years old. For
OL,17,Fthe last three and a half years,
OL,18,FMartin has been joined by youngest
OL,19,Fdaughter, Romney, who is 25.
