OL,3,CFarmers' protest: 'I've never seen
OL,4,Cfarmers come together with such
OL,5,Cemotion'
OL,7,FBut while Romney was once excited
OL,8,Fabout taking over from her father, now
OL,9,Fshe's fearful about what the future
OL,10,Fholds. The Government's planned
OL,11,Finheritance tax changes for farmers
OL,12,Fmeans she could have an incredible tax
OL,13,Fbill to pay.
OL,15,FRomney says: "It's a huge
OL,16,Fresponsibility to take on a farm and
OL,17,Fif you're not going to perhaps be
OL,18,Fearning lots but have this huge bill
OL,19,Fto pay, it's a huge thing to take on."
