OL,7,FMartin and Romney will join other
OL,8,Ffarmers in London on Tuesday 19
OL,9,FNovember.
OL,11,FMartin says: "This is about the
OL,12,Fcontinuity of the family businesses,
OL,13,Fit isn't just about just farming. I've
OL,14,Fnever known a moment in farming crisis
OL,15,Fwhen farmers have come to gather so
OL,16,Frapidly and so instantly and with such
OL,17,Femotion as this issue."
