OL,7,FThe government says that up to #3
OL,8,Fmillion can be passed on by two people
OL,9,Ffree of inheritance tax. Anything
OL,10,Fbeyond that will be taxed at 20%,
OL,11,Frather than the usual 40% .
OL,13,FBut The NFU says it puts the future of
OL,14,Fmany farm businesses under threat.
