OL,3,CFarmers' protest: 'I've never seen
OL,4,Cfarmers come together with such
OL,5,Cemotion'
OL,7,FAfter decades of tightening margins,
OL,8,Frecord inflation, extreme weather and
OL,9,Fincreased production costs, many
OL,10,Ffarmers and growers are at breaking
OL,11,Fpoint, unable to absorb any more cost
OL,12,Fburden.
OL,14,FThe NFU has also warned that the
OL,15,Fchanges announced in the Budget could
OL,16,Fincrease food costs to consumers,
OL,17,Fadding pressure to many still
OL,18,Fexperiencing the cost-of-living crisis.
