OL,4,Cfarmers come together with such
OL,5,Cemotion'
OL,7,FIn a statement the Government said:
OL,8,F"With public services crumbling, a
OL,9,F#22bn fiscal hole inherited from the
OL,10,Fprevious government and 40% of
OL,11,FAgricultural Property Relief going to
OL,12,Fthe 7% wealthiest claimants, we made a
OL,13,Fdifficult decision to ensure the
OL,14,Frelief is fiscally sustainable.
OL,16,F"Around 500 claims each year will be
OL,17,Fimpacted and farm-owning couples can
OL,18,Fpass on up to #3m without paying any
OL,19,Finheritance tax - this is a fair and
OL,20,Fbalanced approach."
